The paper discusses the identification of landmark publications in various Web of Science subject categories, which involves analyzing citation counts and using software for big data analyses in bibliometrics. This suggests that the paper may be relevant to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), social and information networks (cs.SI), and databases (cs.DB).
